alue":"21-样式要点","line":46,"column":0,"depth":3},"22-尺寸说明以源码宏为准":{"type":"header","text":"2.2 尺寸说明（以源码宏为准）","value":"22-尺寸说明以源码宏为准","line":54,"column":0,"depth":3},"3-模式图标动效lv_mode_panel_icon_anim":{"type":"header","text":"3. 模式图标动效（LV_MODE_PANEL_ICON_ANIM）","value":"3-模式图标动效lv_mode_panel_icon_anim","line":62,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-开关":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 开关","value":"31-开关","line":64,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-本会话演进对照":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 本会话演进（对照）","value":"32-本会话演进对照","line":71,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-行为说明":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 行为说明","value":"33-行为说明","line":76,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-开机花屏雪花--gram-未初始化":{"type":"header","text":"4. 开机花屏（雪花 / GRAM 未初始化）","value":"4-开机花屏雪花--gram-未初始化","line":83,"column":0,"depth":2},"5-附录本会话问答":{"type":"header","text":"5. 附录（本会话问答）","value":"5-附录本会话问答","line":91,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-相关文件速查":{"type":"header","text":"6. 相关文件速查","value":"6-相关文件速查","line":101,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"dev-log-index","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"lvgl-模式卡片六模式图标资源与动效--开发总结\">LVGL 模式卡片、六模式图标资源与动效 — 开发总结<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lvgl-模式卡片六模式图标资源与动效--开发总结\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"lvgl-模式卡片六模式图标资源与动效--开发总结-1\">LVGL 模式卡片、六模式图标资源与动效 — 开发总结<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lvgl-模式卡片六模式图标资源与动效--开发总结-1\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>本文汇总本会话周期内针对 <strong>BK7252n + LVGL 主桌面六模式</strong> 的相关开发与排查结论。<br>\n<strong>实现细节以当前仓库内源码为准</strong>（例如 <code>MAIN_MODE_PANEL_W/H</code>、动效开关默认值可能随后续提交调整）。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-六模式图标资源png--bmp--固件\">1. 六模式图标资源（PNG → BMP → 固件）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-六模式图标资源png--bmp--固件\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"11-文件位置\">1.1 文件位置<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#11-文件位置\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>用途</th><th>路径</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>源 PNG（可按模式替换）</td><td><code>applications/images/mode_jpg/</code></td></tr><tr><td>生成脚本</td><td><code>tools/scripts/gen_mode_icons_bmp.py</code></td></tr><tr><td>嵌入固件的 C 数组</td><td><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>对外声明</td><td><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.h</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h3 id=\"12-生成规则脚本\">1.2 生成规则（脚本）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#12-生成规则脚本\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>顺序</strong>：与 <code>lv_example_meter.c</code> 中 <code>mode_icon_dsc_for_idx()</code> 一致 — 动漫 → 卡通 → 水墨画 → 线条画 → 简笔画 → 素描。</li>\n<li><strong>命名回退</strong>：每个模式优先 <code>&#x3C;stem>.png</code>，若无则用 <code>&#x3C;stem>1.png</code>（便于目录里混用「动漫.png / 动漫1.png」）。</li>\n<li><strong>尺寸</strong>：统一缩放为 <strong>100×100</strong>，输出 <strong>24 位 BMP</strong>，在 <code>lv_img_dsc_t</code> 中使用 <strong><code>LV_IMG_CF_RAW</code></strong>（整文件嵌入，由 LVGL BMP 解码）。</li>\n<li><strong>透明通道</strong>：工程 <strong><code>LV_COLOR_DEPTH</code> 为 16</strong> 时，嵌入式 BMP 路径下难以做到真正意义上的 Alpha 合成；脚本对 <strong>RGBA</strong> 图源采用 <strong><code>#FFF9C4</code>（与桌面黄卡片同色）</strong> 做垫色合成，避免白边；<strong>纯 RGB</strong> 图源不做垫色。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>脚本内常量 <strong><code>MATTE_RGB = (255, 249, 196)</code></strong> 应与桌面卡片背景一致（如 <strong><code>UI_DESKTOP_CARD_BG_HEX</code> / <code>0xFFF9C4</code></strong>）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"13-重新生成命令\">1.3 重新生成命令<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#13-重新生成命令\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">python3 tools/scripts/gen_mode_icons_bmp.py\nscons --beken<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>bk7252n -j8\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-模式卡片-ui黄底--圆形\">2. 模式卡片 UI（黄底 + 圆形）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-模式卡片-ui黄底--圆形\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"21-样式要点\">2.1 样式要点<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#21-样式要点\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>背景色</strong>：浅黄 <strong><code>#FFF9C4</code></strong>。</li>\n<li><strong>形状</strong>：<strong>正圆</strong> — 宽与高相等时使用 <strong><code>LV_RADIUS_CIRCLE</code></strong>，并配合 <strong><code>lv_obj_set_style_clip_corner(..., true)</code></strong>，避免子控件画出方角。</li>\n<li><strong>两处需一致</strong>：\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>main_mode_shell_style</code></strong>：主桌面当前模式外壳。</li>\n<li><strong><code>voice_panel_attach_card</code></strong>：语音流程里同风格衬底卡片。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"22-尺寸说明以源码宏为准\">2.2 尺寸说明（以源码宏为准）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#22-尺寸说明以源码宏为准\"></a></h3>\n<p>会话中曾用 <strong>135×135</strong>；当前仓库若为 <strong>150×150</strong> 等，以 <strong><code>MAIN_MODE_PANEL_W</code> / <code>MAIN_MODE_PANEL_H</code></strong>（及 <strong><code>VOICE_CARD_PANEL_*</code></strong>）为准。</p>\n<p>图标 <strong>hub</strong> 典型为 <strong><code>MAIN_MODE_PANEL_W - 8</code> × <code>102</code></strong>，图标 <strong>100×100</strong>，标题底部对齐（如 <strong><code>MODE_PANEL_LABEL_BOTTOM_Y_OFS</code></strong>）。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-模式图标动效lv_mode_panel_icon_anim\">3. 模式图标动效（<code>LV_MODE_PANEL_ICON_ANIM</code>）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-模式图标动效lv_mode_panel_icon_anim\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-开关\">3.1 开关<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-开关\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>宏：<strong><code>LV_MODE_PANEL_ICON_ANIM</code></strong>（<code>lv_example_meter.c</code>）。</li>\n<li><strong><code>1</code></strong>：对当前 <strong><code>s_mode_fx_hub[idx]</code></strong> 启动 <code>lv_anim</code>（具体组合见 <code>mode_panel_img_anim_start()</code>）。</li>\n<li><strong><code>0</code></strong>：编译期裁掉动效实现。</li>\n<li>可 <strong><code> -DLV_MODE_PANEL_ICON_ANIM=0</code></strong> 覆盖。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"32-本会话演进对照\">3.2 本会话演进（对照）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-本会话演进对照\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>曾关动效 / 再开，并加大位移、缩短周期便于观察。</li>\n<li>曾改为全员 <strong>TY 弹跳 + TX 摆动</strong>、<strong>去掉透明度呼吸</strong>（若仓库后续又混用透明度，以当前 <code>switch (idx)</code> 为准）。</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"33-行为说明\">3.3 行为说明<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-行为说明\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>同一时间只显示 <strong>当前模式</strong> 一张卡片，动效只作用当前 <strong>idx</strong> 的 hub。</li>\n<li>动效作用在 <strong>hub</strong>，减轻对 <strong><code>lv_img</code> transform</strong> 与 layer RAM 的压力。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-开机花屏雪花--gram-未初始化\">4. 开机花屏（雪花 / GRAM 未初始化）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-开机花屏雪花--gram-未初始化\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>原因</strong>：GRAM 随机内容被扫出或背光过早。</li>\n<li><strong><code>beken378/driver/lcd/lcd_driver.c</code></strong>：<code>drv_lcd_open()</code> 中注释建议 <strong><code>_lcd_clear(COLOR_BLACK)</code></strong> 后再亮背光（是否启用看该行是否仍注释）。</li>\n<li><strong><code>applications/main.c</code></strong>：关背光 → <code>drv_lcd_open()</code> → LVGL/UI → 再开背光；仍花屏时核对背光 GPIO 极性与其它提前拉高背光的代码。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-附录本会话问答\">5. 附录（本会话问答）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-附录本会话问答\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>主题</th><th>要点</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Flash 余量</td><td>分区大小见 <code>config.json</code> / <code>tools/scripts/post_action.py</code>；<strong><code>wc -c rtthread.bin</code></strong> 得镜像大小；余量 ≈ 分区 ? bin（视对齐而定）。</td></tr><tr><td>heap / memheap / ITCM</td><td>heap 为动态内存概念；memheap 为 RT-Thread 堆实现；ITCM 见 <strong><code>link.lds</code></strong>，与 malloc 堆不同。</td></tr><tr><td>CPU 占用</td><td><strong><code>list_thread</code> / <code>ps</code></strong> 看线程与<strong>栈</strong>占用百分比；整 CPU 可参考 <strong><code>rt-thread/examples/kernel/cpuusage.c</code></strong> 自行挂 Shell。</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-相关文件速查\">6. 相关文件速查<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-相关文件速查\"></a></h2>\n<pre><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c\napplications/images/mode_icons_bmp.c\ntools/scripts/gen_mode_icons_bmp.py\nbeken378/driver/lcd/lcd_driver.c\napplications/main.c\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<p><em>梳理日期：2026-05-07。</em></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/dev-log-index\">开发日志</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/6d428def14b8ffdc828f43\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目交接资料</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目开发记录总纲</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"项目开发笔记","desc":"项目开发笔记（Dendron 多项目知识库）","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"config":{"global":{"enableChildLinks":false}},"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"2c8c2178e78de3c5c6be3ee4a51e2853","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":42},"end":{"line":6,"column":9,"offset":48},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":3,"offset":60},"end":{"line":7,"column":23,"offset":80},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机"}}],"anchors":{},"children":["c1bs7wsjfbhb0zipaywqv1","projects"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n按**项目**组织的固件与软件开发文档（Dendron）。\n\n**项目**\n\n- [[项目]] — 全部项目索引\n- [[项目.BK7252N-AI打印机]] — BK7252N AI 打印机固件（RT-Thread + LVGL）\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"}],"enableXVaultWikiLink":true,"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","